entries.femaleVariant: But, sweetie, why do this? You got so much potential. You'd make a great techie.
Daddy, please... This is, like, the millionth time...
And I'll bring it up another million times. I don't want some stranger to hurt my little angel...
Dad, us Moxes have each other's backs. We look out for one another.
I--I'll getcha an interview with my boss at the plant. You always dreamed of working with machines.
Right. The same filthy, leaky machines that gave mom cancer? Those machines?
I'd rather choke on a stranger's dick than choke on those fumes.
